In my vision I see a woman...or I think there a woman, woman shapped with a...moon for a head.
join starlight left
- What?
	???: Do you not recall? you just fell out of the sky? It was quite a sight I tell you.
	???: Oh I'm sorry you must be confused. Allow me to introduce myself please.
- Who are you?
	???: Oh my pardons, where are my manners?
starlight: My name is [i]starlight[/i]. I am one of the inhabitants of the [color=red]Grand woods[/color]...you actually landed on my front lawn legally speaking...
starlight: But do not fret! I will not file any complants with you!
starlight: I think falling headfirst into the soil is punishment enough...
- How did I get here?
	starlight: Hm? Well you fell out of the sky...
	starlight: ...OH i think i got it!
- I must have fainted...
	starlight: hm? Fainted you say? OH that would make sense!
starlight: The way I see it my friend you are either\:
starlight: You are some kind of Demonic entity here to bring destruction to my property.
starlight: or...
starlight: You my probably concused friend, are dreaming.
- Dreaming?
	starlight: Yes indeed! You fell asleep and everything you see here is a creation from your psyche. A reflection of your wonderful mind.
	starlight: That would definatly explain a lot of things...
	starlight: ...like Steve.
	starlight: But I digress.
- I think you were right the first time
	starlight: ....
	starlight: ........
	starlight: Oh-ho you little trickster you!
	starlight: Everyone knows that Demonic Entities can not tell you they are a Demonic Entity!
	starlight: That is one of their laws you know.
	starlight: So yes, than you must be dreaming. Only Explenation!
starlight: You have fallen asleep, and are probably wanting to get back to your body I would presume?
- That would be nice...
- Sure...
starlight: Perfect!
starlight: Now unfortunately because you are now aware that this is a dream you can't just wake your self up normally...Dream logic you know how it can function yes?
starlight: However! I am fairly confident I know the way out! You just need to go through the dream world and find the exit!
- And where is the exit?
	starlight: I...am not certain.
- That is very discriptive.
	Look I just found out my existance is a fictisous fabrication. Give me a break.
starlight: My guess would be beyond the [color=red]Darken Bridges[/color]. You can get there through the large gate north of us.
starlight: The gate might be locked however, one of those eyeless scoundrals tried to steal my pigs...It did not even have a mouth!
starlight: Oh apolagizes,  I am rambling again.
starlight: If it is locked you can talk to [color=red]Red[/color]. They have the key to the gate and can help you.
